  <brief_title>Effect of Adaptive Servoventilation on Cardiac Function in Chronic Heart Failure and Cheyne-Stokes Respiration</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Adaptive Servoventilation on Cardiac Function, Exercise Tolerance and Quality of Life in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure and Cheyne-Stokes Respiration</official_title>
